    "notes": "100kg Beast (Pouncer), jungle walker, #App: 1d6, Treasure: None. Teeth (2d6); armor 2; speed 10m/action; Morale +0. The Komodo dragon is a large venomous lizard that stalks prey on jungle islands. It is highly intelligent and capable of complex hunting tactics. Its preferred hunting method is to envenom its prey, retreat, and wait for the venom to kill the hapless victim. Venom: 10+/4d6 delivered by bite. Takes 1d6 turns to take effect. (Instinct 12, Pack 3)",
